      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Norman Park benefits from consistent demand from families priced out of Balmoral and Hawthorne who still want inner-east character living. Limited listing supply, strong school catchments and the suburb's green credentials along Norman Creek create competitive conditions that support strong sale prices."
      }
